Pre-Game Insights: Frankie Musonda stated that Chipolopolo are going all out against Morocco in their must-win and final 2023 AFCON Group F match.
Zambia is eager to redeem itself after 1-1 draws in their opening two Group F fixtures against DR Congo and Tanzania.
Musonda highlighted the importance of the next game and the team's determination to give their best.
This will be Chipolopolo and The Atlas Lions' third AFCON meeting, with Morocco having an edge with one win and a draw.
